}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(London 2012) was quite the venue but this one, the night matches are going to be spectacular.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(London\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the venue\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"the night matches\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are trying to up (the level at each Games) Asked if the IOC was \\\"comfortable and happy\\\" with Van de Velde's involvement, its spokesman Mark Adams said: \\\"I think to characterise it as \\\"comfortable and happy\\\" would not be correct.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2239078696938586e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2789, \"end\": 2799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298825356, \"rank\": 0.45833333333342063, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"each Games\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"Van de Velde's involvement\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"its spokesman\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a crime occurred some time ago, 10 years ago.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\":